title: Knife Sharpening with Ray Mears + Making Cordage + Cheeta Kill
description:
This is perfect DVD (.ISO) Rip of the Extras from the DVD "Ray Mears Bushcraft Survival Series 1" this includes:

- Knife Sharpening in the Field
- Knife Sharpening at Base Camp
- Making Natural Cordage
- Filming a Cheeta Kill

Learn how to sharpen a knife from the master of the Bushcraft world. In this footage Ray Mears gives you a truly superb, up close lesson in how to sharpen your blade, the right stones and techniques to use.

Appreciate this knowledge and share on to a 1.2 Ratio, Thank you.
